<dd class="field-odd"><p><a class="reference external" href="https://docs.python.org/3/library/typing.html#typing.Iterator" title="(in Python v3.13)"><em>Iterator</em></a>[<a class="reference external" href="https://docs.python.org/3/library/stdtypes.html#bytes" title="(in Python v3.13)">bytes</a>]</p>
</dd>
