<p><span class="versionmodified changed">Changed in version 1.1: </span><code class="docutils literal notranslate"><span class="pre">filename</span></code> may be a <a class="reference external" href="https://docs.python.org/3/library/os.html#os.PathLike" title="(in Python v3.13)"><code class="xref py py-class docutils literal notranslate"><span class="pre">PathLike</span></code></a> object.</p>
