<p><span class="versionmodified changed">Changed in version 1.1: </span>Passing a <a class="reference external" href="https://docs.python.org/3/library/io.html#io.BytesIO" title="(in Python v3.13)"><code class="xref py py-class docutils literal notranslate"><span class="pre">BytesIO</span></code></a> object supports range requests.</p>
