<li><p><strong>kwargs</strong> (<a class="reference external" href="https://docs.python.org/3/library/typing.html#typing.Any" title="(in Python v3.13)"><em>Any</em></a>) – Passed to <a class="reference external" href="https://docs.python.org/3/library/json.html#json.dumps" title="(in Python v3.13)"><code class="xref py py-func docutils literal notranslate"><span class="pre">json.dumps()</span></code></a>.</p></li>
